1
00:00:01,292 --> 00:00:03,837
<c.bg_transparent><i>Alkimia adalah ilmu yang terdiri dari</i></c.bg_transparent>

2
00:00:03,920 --> 00:00:06,423
<c.bg_transparent><i>pengertian, dekonstruksi,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>dan rekonstruksi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

3
00:00:06,506 --> 00:00:09,384
<c.bg_transparent><i>Namun, ilmu ini bukan tak terbatas.</i></c.bg_transparent>

4
00:00:09,467 --> 00:00:12,470
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tak mungkin ciptakan sesuatu</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>dari ketiadaan.</i></c.bg_transparent>

5
00:00:12,804 --> 00:00:18,059
<c.bg_transparent><i>Jika inginkan sesuatu,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>harus korbankan sesuatu yang setara.</i></c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:18,143 --> 00:00:22,522
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pertukaran setara inilah dasar alkimia.</i></c.bg_transparent>

7
00:00:23,231 --> 00:00:27,193
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ada hal tabu dalam alkimia,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>yakni transmutasi manusia.</i></c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:27,277 --> 00:00:30,447
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tak ada yang boleh melanggarnya.</i></c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:48,590 --> 00:00:50,550
<c.bg_transparent>FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:02:01,663 --> 00:02:06,835
<c.bg_transparent><i>Di kota Liore, seorang pendeta</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>ajaran leto memakai alkimia</i></c.bg_transparent>

11
00:02:06,918 --> 00:02:09,254
<c.bg_transparent><i>dengan Batu Bertuah untuk menipu warga.</i></c.bg_transparent>

12
00:02:09,337 --> 00:02:10,922
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saat masuk gerejanya,</i></c.bg_transparent>

13
00:02:11,005 --> 00:02:13,633
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ed dan Al menghentikan rencana jahatnya.</i></c.bg_transparent>

14
00:02:14,425 --> 00:02:17,679
<c.bg_transparent><i>Namun, Batu Bertuah itu palsu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

15
00:02:18,429 --> 00:02:21,307
<c.bg_transparent><i>"Berdiri dan berjalanlah. Terus maju."</i></c.bg_transparent>

16
00:02:21,391 --> 00:02:25,186
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hilang harapan, kata-kata Ed</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>terngingang di hati Rose.</i></c.bg_transparent>

17
00:02:25,895 --> 00:02:30,191
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kata-kata Ed itu pun</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>tertuju pada diri mereka sendiri.</i></c.bg_transparent>

18
00:02:30,275 --> 00:02:33,194
<c.bg_transparent>EPISODE 4, DERITA SEORANG AHLI ALKIMIA</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:02:41,911 --> 00:02:45,832
<c.bg_transparent>Kau Ahli Alkimia Darah Besi,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Basque Grand, 'kan?</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:47,834
<c.bg_transparent>Kau siapa?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:02:48,835 --> 00:02:53,631
<c.bg_transparent>Ahli alkimia yang berpaling dari Tuhan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>harus musnah.</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:02:54,924 --> 00:03:00,597
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, kau pembunuh yang hanya targetkan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ahli Alkimia Negara itu, ya?</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Tapi</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:03:02,182 --> 00:03:05,268
<c.bg_transparent>kau memilih lawan yang salah!</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:03:16,738 --> 00:03:18,406
<c.bg_transparent>Kau cepat. Tapi tak cukup!</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:03:21,659 --> 00:03:23,453
<c.bg_transparent>Sesuai maumu!</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:03:28,208 --> 00:03:30,293
<c.bg_transparent>Tak terlalu sulit.</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:40,887
<c.bg_transparent>Apa-apaan?</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:03:41,971 --> 00:03:43,264
<c.bg_transparent>Mati.</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:03:55,235 --> 00:03:57,111
<c.bg_transparent>Ahli Alkimia Negara lagi?</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:03:57,737 --> 00:04:00,240
<c.bg_transparent>Jelas dia sangat kuat.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:04:01,032 --> 00:04:02,367
<c.bg_transparent>Mayor, jaga dirimu.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:05,870
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin kau target berikutnya.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:04:06,329 --> 00:04:07,413
<c.bg_transparent>Baik.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:04:14,003 --> 00:04:16,714
<c.bg_transparent>Yang Mulia Fuhrer, kenapa ke sini?</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:04:18,258 --> 00:04:20,176
<c.bg_transparent>Aku mendengar laporannya.</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:04:21,344 --> 00:04:24,639
<c.bg_transparent>Letnan Kolonel Hughes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kau penanggung jawab kasus ini?</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:04:24,722 --> 00:04:28,685
<c.bg_transparent>- Ya, Pak.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Jika butuh bantuan, minta saja.</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:04:29,269 --> 00:04:32,689
<c.bg_transparent>Kita harus menindak pengkhianat.</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:04:34,023 --> 00:04:34,899
<c.bg_transparent>Baik, Pak.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:39,153
<c.bg_transparent>Letnan Breda.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:41,990
<c.bg_transparent>Baik. Astaga.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:04:42,407 --> 00:04:45,451
<c.bg_transparent>Kolonel menumpuk pekerjaannya lagi, ya?</c.bg_transparent>

43
00:04:45,994 --> 00:04:48,621
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, Havoc, bantu selesaikan setengahnya.</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:04:48,705 --> 00:04:50,707
<c.bg_transparent>Aku juga banyak pekerjaan.</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:04:51,332 --> 00:04:54,711
<c.bg_transparent>- Lihat, siapa ini?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Letnan Yoki.</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:04:55,420 --> 00:05:00,091
<c.bg_transparent>Dia bajingan pencari keuntungan sendiri</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>di konsesi tambang batubara Youswell.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:05:00,174 --> 00:05:04,137
<c.bg_transparent>Elric bersaudara membongkarnya,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kini dia dalam pelarian.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:05:04,846 --> 00:05:07,432
<c.bg_transparent>Sersan Satu Fuery, bagaimana radionya?</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:05:07,932 --> 00:05:11,894
<c.bg_transparent>Penerima radionya rusak, harus kuganti.</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:05:15,481 --> 00:05:17,358
<c.bg_transparent>Edward! Alphonse!</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:05:17,442 --> 00:05:21,487
<c.bg_transparent>Selamat datang kembali.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kolonel menunggu kalian.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:05:23,156 --> 00:05:26,326
<c.bg_transparent>Kasus Liore teratasi berkat kalian.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:05:26,409 --> 00:05:27,744
<c.bg_transparent>Terima kasih.</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:05:27,827 --> 00:05:30,830
<c.bg_transparent>Tak masalah, tak kami lakukan untukmu.</c.bg_transparent>

55
00:05:30,913 --> 00:05:34,000
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, Batu Bertuah itu tak berguna juga?</c.bg_transparent>

56
00:05:38,379 --> 00:05:43,426
<c.bg_transparent>Batu itu palsu, tapi setidaknya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kekuatannya luar biasa,</c.bg_transparent>

57
00:05:43,926 --> 00:05:46,554
<c.bg_transparent>bisa transmutasi khimaira besar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dan lainnya.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:05:46,637 --> 00:05:49,557
<c.bg_transparent>Aku ingin tahu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>bagaimana caranya memakainya.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:53,644
<c.bg_transparent>Transmutasi hidup bidang baru bagi kita,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>belum terlalu kita pahami.</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:05:53,728 --> 00:05:56,272
<c.bg_transparent>Tetap saja menarik, 'kan?</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:05:56,606 --> 00:05:57,523
<c.bg_transparent>Jika diteliti,</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:05:57,607 --> 00:06:00,860
<c.bg_transparent>mungkin bisa berguna</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengembalikan tubuh kita.</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:06:01,861 --> 00:06:04,113
<c.bg_transparent>Kalian perlu bantuan spesialis?</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:06:05,782 --> 00:06:09,327
<c.bg_transparent>Ahli Alkimia Perajut Nyawa, Shou Tucker.</c.bg_transparent>

65
00:06:09,410 --> 00:06:12,246
<c.bg_transparent>Peneliti transmutasi khimaira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Akan kukenalkan.</c.bg_transparent>

66
00:06:12,747 --> 00:06:14,582
<c.bg_transparent>Kau mau serepot itu, Kolonel?</c.bg_transparent>

67
00:06:14,665 --> 00:06:17,293
<c.bg_transparent>Dia merencanakan sesuatu!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Pasti ada sesuatu!</c.bg_transparent>

68
00:06:17,377 --> 00:06:21,464
<c.bg_transparent>Jangan mencurigaiku!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ini balas budiku untuk kasus Liore.</c.bg_transparent>

69
00:06:21,547 --> 00:06:24,175
<c.bg_transparent>Mengerikan berutang budi padamu.</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:06:25,885 --> 00:06:27,428
<c.bg_transparent>2 tahun lalu Tucker sukses</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:06:27,512 --> 00:06:30,431
<c.bg_transparent>mentransmutasi khimaira</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang paham bahasa manusia</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:06:30,515 --> 00:06:32,934
<c.bg_transparent>dan mendapat gelar Ahli Alkimia Negara.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:06:33,393 --> 00:06:38,272
<c.bg_transparent>Paham bahasa manusia?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maksudmu bisa bicara? Khimaira?</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:06:38,398 --> 00:06:40,691
<c.bg_transparent>Ya, kurasa bisa.</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:06:41,442 --> 00:06:42,693
<c.bg_transparent>Hanya satu kalimat.</c.bg_transparent>

76
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:45,238
<c.bg_transparent>"Aku ingin mati."</c.bg_transparent>

77
00:06:47,073 --> 00:06:50,076
<c.bg_transparent>Setelah itu, makhluk itu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tak mau makan dan mati.</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:06:54,664 --> 00:06:56,582
<c.bg_transparent>Besar sekali rumahnya.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:07:01,087 --> 00:07:03,131
<c.bg_transparent>Kakak.</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:07:04,924 --> 00:07:10,680
<c.bg_transparent>- Banyak tamu!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Nina, harusnya kamu mengikatnya.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:07:13,724 --> 00:07:15,560
<c.bg_transparent>Maaf berantakan.</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:07:15,643 --> 00:07:19,272
<c.bg_transparent>Rumahku seperti ini</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sejak istriku meninggalkanku.</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:07:26,237 --> 00:07:29,782
<c.bg_transparent>Sekali lagi,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>senang bertemu denganmu, Edward.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:07:29,866 --> 00:07:32,827
<c.bg_transparent>Aku Ahli Alkimia Perajut Nyawa,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Shou Tucker.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:07:33,411 --> 00:07:36,539
<c.bg_transparent>Dia tertarik mentransmutasi makhluk hidup.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:07:36,622 --> 00:07:38,916
<c.bg_transparent>Dia bilang ingin melihat risetmu.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,169
<c.bg_transparent>Tentu, dengan senang hati.</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:07:42,628 --> 00:07:44,255
<c.bg_transparent>- Tapi...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:07:45,047 --> 00:07:47,258
<c.bg_transparent>Kalau mau lihat keahlianku,</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:07:47,341 --> 00:07:50,178
<c.bg_transparent>perlihatkan juga kebolehanmu.</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:53,181
<c.bg_transparent>Seperti itulah ahli kimia.</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:07:53,890 --> 00:07:56,559
<c.bg_transparent>Kenapa kau tertarik</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tranmutasi makhluk hidup?</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:07:57,685 --> 00:08:00,354
<c.bg_transparent>- Yah, dia...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Kolonel.</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:08:03,649 --> 00:08:08,446
<c.bg_transparent>Kau mentransmutasi ibumu?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Padahal kau baru 11 tahun?</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:08:09,363 --> 00:08:13,451
<c.bg_transparent>Begitu. Karena itu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kau Ahli Alkimia Bertubuh Besi.</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:08:14,952 --> 00:08:16,913
<c.bg_transparent>Pengalamanmu buruk juga, ya?</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:08:22,502 --> 00:08:24,921
<c.bg_transparent>Entah akan berguna atau tidak,</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:08:25,546 --> 00:08:28,257
<c.bg_transparent>tapi silakan masuk ke laboratoriumku.</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:08:34,222 --> 00:08:36,224
<c.bg_transparent>Yah, ini memalukan.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:08:36,849 --> 00:08:41,354
<c.bg_transparent>Aku dianggap ahli soal khimaira,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tapi nyatanya</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:08:41,771 --> 00:08:43,856
<c.bg_transparent>tidak selancar itu.</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:08:46,692 --> 00:08:48,819
<c.bg_transparent>Astaga. Hebat!</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:08:48,903 --> 00:08:51,405
<c.bg_transparent>Ini ruang referensiku,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>silakan berkeliling.</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:08:51,906 --> 00:08:56,827
<c.bg_transparent>- Baik, kumulai dari sini.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Aku dari sini.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:08:58,037 --> 00:09:02,166
<c.bg_transparent>Aku kembali ke markas, sore nanti</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kukirim petugas menjemput kalian.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:09:05,753 --> 00:09:07,713
<c.bg_transparent>Mereka fokus sekali, ya?</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:09:07,797 --> 00:09:10,174
<c.bg_transparent>Mereka tak dengar apa pun lagi.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:15,555
<c.bg_transparent>Ada anak berbakat di luar sana, ya?</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:09:40,621 --> 00:09:42,873
<c.bg_transparent>Naik menjulang tinggi!</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:09:44,959 --> 00:09:47,587
<c.bg_transparent>Al! Sedang apa kau?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:09:47,795 --> 00:09:50,006
<c.bg_transparent>Nina sepertinya ingin bermain.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:09:50,089 --> 00:09:53,593
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, ingat tujuan kita ke sini!</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:09:58,514 --> 00:10:01,601
<c.bg_transparent>Alexander bilang dia juga ingin bermain.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:10:03,227 --> 00:10:04,395
<c.bg_transparent>Lancang benar kau.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:10:05,104 --> 00:10:08,774
<c.bg_transparent>Katanya singa bahkan memakai</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seluruh tenaga mengejar kelinci.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:10:09,358 --> 00:10:14,238
<c.bg_transparent>Karena itu, aku, Edward Elric,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>akan memakai tubuh dan jiwaku</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:10:14,322 --> 00:10:16,699
<c.bg_transparent>untuk menghabisimu, anjing sial!</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:22,288
<c.bg_transparent>Halo, Pak, aku datang menjemput.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:26,834
<c.bg_transparent>Kau sedang apa?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:10:26,917 --> 00:10:30,755
<c.bg_transparent>Yah, bisa disebut istirahat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>setelah meneliti data.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:10:32,006 --> 00:10:34,258
<c.bg_transparent>Kau menemukan referensi bagus?</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:10:36,344 --> 00:10:37,595
<c.bg_transparent>Besok mampir lagi.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:41,599
<c.bg_transparent>- Besok kau datang lagi?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Lanjut besok, ya, Nina.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:10:41,682 --> 00:10:42,683
<c.bg_transparent>Ya!</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:10:44,435 --> 00:10:47,688
<c.bg_transparent>Pak Tucker, ada pesan dari kolonel.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:10:47,772 --> 00:10:51,651
<c.bg_transparent>Katanya, "Jangan lupa,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sebentar lagi Hari Penilaian."</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:10:52,652 --> 00:10:54,904
<c.bg_transparent>Ya, aku tahu.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:56,530
<c.bg_transparent>Aku permisi.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,704
<c.bg_transparent>Ayah.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:11:05,164 --> 00:11:07,291
<c.bg_transparent>"Penilaian" itu apa?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:12,338
<c.bg_transparent>Ahli Alkimia Negara harus melaporkan</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:11:12,421 --> 00:11:15,341
<c.bg_transparent>hasil penelitian mereka setahun sekali.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:11:17,009 --> 00:11:21,055
<c.bg_transparent>Hasil evaluasi tahun lalu ayah</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tak terlalu bagus.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:11:21,138 --> 00:11:25,476
<c.bg_transparent>Kalau tahun ini gagal,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gelar Alkimia Negara ayah dicabut.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:31,774
<c.bg_transparent>Apa? Ayah pasti bisa!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ayah selalu belajar tekun!</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:11:33,526 --> 00:11:35,820
<c.bg_transparent><i>Benar, aku harus berusaha keras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

137
00:11:37,822 --> 00:11:41,158
<c.bg_transparent><i>Atau aku tak punya apa pun lagi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:11:46,747 --> 00:11:49,166
<c.bg_transparent>Apa? Ibumu pergi dua tahun lalu?</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:11:50,042 --> 00:11:53,421
<c.bg_transparent>Ayah bilang ibu kembali</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ke rumah orang tuanya.</c.bg_transparent>

